      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities replicate the ASTM F1717 test protocol using production-equivalent hardware. The experimental scenario closely mirrors the intended computational use scenario, supporting relevance of the validation evidence."
