    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a Medium model risk assessment. The single below-required factor (Test conditions) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the single-condition F1717 protocol is consistent with regulatory precedent for this device class and that residual uncertainty is acceptable for the stated decision. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
